fields.search:
SELECT artist_lastfm, count(artist_lastfm) as cn
FROM ((
SELECT artist_lastfm, tag_lastfm
FROM `artists`.`artists` lateral view explode(split(tags_lastfm,';')) tags_lastfm AS tag_lastfm) as tb1
INNER JOIN
(SELECT tag_lastfm, sum(listeners_lastfm) as sum_linsteners
FROM `artists`.`artists` lateral view explode(split(tags_lastfm,';')) tags_lastfm AS tag_lastfm GROUP BY tag_lastfm ORDER BY sum_linsteners DESC LIMIT 10) as tb2
ON tb1.tag_lastfm = tb2.tag_lastfm) 
GROUP BY tb1.artist_lastfm 
ORDER BY cn 
DESC LIMIT 10
